Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们梦想着  改变未来的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}杂音中  传来你的哭泣声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭开我  欢笑之下的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能决定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐着  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们渴求着前往未来的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却为此在过去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑着的此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:31.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色の午後は　ママレイドティーとビスケット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:37.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}散らかったトランプで　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:46.44,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ夢の続きを占いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:54.92,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いくつのドア　開くのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.87,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…サガシモノ　何処ニアル？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:06.94,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.10,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:18.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づけば　私は迷子で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:26.83,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密の暗号　君だけに送ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:30.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はやく見つけて　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:35.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私はここだよ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:31.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色的午后  品尝着柚子茶和饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.39,0:22:37.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}收起散落一地的纸牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:46.44,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}来  占卜梦境的后续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.26,0:22:54.92,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会打开多少扇大门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:02.87,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…寻找的东西  究竟在何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.89,0:23:06.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:11.10,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只追逐着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:18.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这才发现我迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.52,0:23:26.83,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只向你送去  秘密的暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.24,0:23:30.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快点找到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:35.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我在这里哦。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等沉重的气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小鬼的妹妹的学校回来后就一直那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇上了巴司卡维尔的人  就那么受打击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  原因好像是埃利奥特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那个容易发脾气的小少爷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也在同一所学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说救了奥兹大人的就是他和他的侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问一下关于那首曲子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:24.89,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}变迁的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以  能不能告诉我呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩联弹过吧  就是那时弹的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首曲子是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲名叫「蕾茜」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个  差不多该告诉我你的名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道该怎么称呼你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对艾达的那个态度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因为两家不和的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么他要是知道我是贝萨流斯家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必也会发怒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  总觉得不能对这家伙撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我稍微注意一下气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  我刚才可是遇到大麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也遇上了很麻烦的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之间  被一大群女学生围住…痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法抽身…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太让人羡慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在这学校上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我大吃一惊啊  没想到会在这里相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  最近还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你这家伙会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奥特  你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你那身装扮是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都24岁的人了  还穿学生制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恬不知耻！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（说得一点没错）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会认识这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢对他动粗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你  我也不会原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹·贝萨流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝萨流斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  奥兹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我听说奥兹·贝萨流斯在十年前就死了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太荒谬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了  里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奥特   我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来烦我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才会信你们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:27.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（嘎叽嘎叽…）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样  到最后都没说上话就告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  基尔巴特君是因为完全被弟弟疏远了而在消沉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一位…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝小姐  在为什么事生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和平常一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的大胃无用女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴  布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  艾莉丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么烦恼的话  就和我谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:16.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（轰轰轰…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.87,0:06:18.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（依靠动物的本能察觉到了危险）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肯陪你玩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说那家伙最近缺少作为仆人的自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前丢下我一人  去陪小丑喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.76,0:06:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还对着自己妹妹  嘿嘿地傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:45.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（嘎叽嘎叽…）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为莫名其妙的家伙而闷闷不乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊  那家伙明明是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么总是想着别人的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那也就是说…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太·美·了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了  艾莉丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是少女啊  这就是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直太让人心动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…心动？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  这种感情叫作「吃醋」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么  好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  要说味道的话  据说是酸酸甜甜的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢吃酸的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  艾莉丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种酸甜的感觉正是浪漫不可缺少的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫是什么  好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  据说是很甜蜜的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的少女开关被按下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就先告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等一下  布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:51.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（呵呵呵呵…）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要全力帮助艾莉丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没说要让你们两个家伙帮我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  之前就感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝小姐完全没叫过我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  试着叫我「夏罗大姐姐」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要叫大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种细节就不要在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开…开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要叫你大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快  快·点·叫·嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（轰轰轰…）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:30.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（依靠动物的本能察觉到了危险  之二）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏…夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:38.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(820,0)}（夏罗看到的幻觉）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了没  布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像有了个妹妹的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看  都只是个在调戏年轻人的大妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:57.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（布雷克的死前讯息是「千根针」写到一半，详见DVD特典）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  艾莉丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来学学关于浪漫的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐会很温柔地教导你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学习浪漫的圣经
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如这本小说里的一段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你哭泣时的丑态明明就只能让身为饲主的我看到」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「见到谁都会摇尾巴的贱狗需要好好调教呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  这和我现在的情况不是一模一样么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  那家伙怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…夏罗大姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  艾莉丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女主人公为了得到他的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用了所有可用的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将竞争对手一个个排除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.83,0:09:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的结局是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  为什么把书合上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:10:01.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（心跳心跳…）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是刚才那个镜头  对艾莉丝来说还有点早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻这种程度的事  我已经和奥兹做过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个披着兔子皮的狼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为违法契约者是由得到灵体的血来完成契约的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:18.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接…接接…接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹他…接…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌啊  奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是定契约时的事  直接说清楚就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会让我解释的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  我不是兔子  艾莉丝才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹…接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥斯卡叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在想是谁呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是涉嫌偷窃女生制服而被逮捕的变态大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛说出来啊  扎克西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被女士们用轻蔑的眼光看着  都快让人上瘾了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:04.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（呀哈哈哈）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这超级M
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还带了果汁来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  虽说这次没弄清楚艾达的心上人到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总之大家都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想庆祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  快  大家都拿起杯子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  庆祝大家平安无事  干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…不管怎么看这液体都…  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是加入了酒精的果汁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们一般都称这种东西为「酒」哦  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小事就不要在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你都已经25岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:06.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（25岁）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  话是这么说没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}（24岁）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200}（人偶  20岁以上）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:11.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200}（也许看不出来  但也是20岁以上）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0}（根本不是人而是灵体）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（没有未成年人！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  奥兹也已经25岁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烦哦  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看  艾莉丝起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…艾莉丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:45.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（替身）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这样啊  艾莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（钮扣被扯掉的声音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中指和食指
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.96,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（各位观众绝对不要模仿哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  她完全喝醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗帮帮我吧  艾莉丝她喝醉了很不妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮你？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让我帮你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跪下来求我吧  你这只猪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人  而且好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全神智不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔的酒量一直都很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（基尔巴特大人  那是个花瓶）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是  总是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（为什么对我吼）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把别人的发型称作海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  海藻头是很伟大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了就找茬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:58.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上帽子现在很流行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗  你这笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（这边也？）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  我到底哪里笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很笨  你连这都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底哪里笨了  你给我好好解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:15.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（抽泣抽泣）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里笨了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（基尔巴特看到的幻觉）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么看都是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（哈哈哈哈…）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  封印解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喝醉了  就放松警惕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死海产品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许和我的仆人黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦  他不是你的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我重要的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这家伙是我的私有物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:15:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你啊  笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（推卸责任）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你监禁在小黑屋里  让你寂寞死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（又是「兔子会因寂寞而死」的迷信）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从根本上来讲  这要怪你对我的仆人出手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多开始觉得烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹那家伙  又在被扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独角兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉丝  基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥·兹·大·人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:52.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,700)}（心跳心跳…）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:56.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}（果然是遗传么…）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蕾茜」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来的话  埃利奥特也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都烂醉如泥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也差不多想睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样说  但其实布雷克完全没有喝醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个不讨人喜欢的小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙夸奖真是荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么要特意装醉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那样的话  会破坏在场的气氛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:57.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要这种奖励啊  你们这群猪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上居然存在布雷克都会注意到的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止一点  小心我拍飞你哦  奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是觉得酒量好的人很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是什么好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多么想醉  都醉不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是为了警告自己不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一直紧绷着神经的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温顺的奥兹君只会让人觉得恶心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许真的是那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许侮辱我的主人  布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要找我茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁找茬了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  我有话…  想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  拜托你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请珍惜自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很伤心  很伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉找茬接下来是一醉就哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这酒品太普通了  一点都不好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp1}boku{\fsp22}　{\fsp1}ore{\fsp51}　{\r}\N我…？我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（boku是基尔小时候的自称，比较青涩；ore是他现在的自称）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…到底是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆试试看「咱」怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「吾」或者「偶」「基露露」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷克  不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  基尔  你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你背负着这种重担啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在开始我也会努力背负一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽量不依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  我想从了解开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事  大家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  下次和我说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事  奈特雷家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这十年来发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真是…  虽说不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但变得相当可爱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你不就可以少辛苦一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.04,0:20:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要讨厌埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并没有做错什么  这点他也很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要怎么说才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奥特他…  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  人很聪明  性格上却是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有缘再会  奥兹·贝萨流斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  总有一天一定可以再相见的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在那时不会被骂  能在他面前昂首挺胸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要按照我自己的方式前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那家伙还有很多话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是关于这首曲子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有很多想问的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧  埃利奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利奥特？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点头晕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做了那个梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整幢房子在燃烧  大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我站在那片血泊中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.90,0:21:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的剑  沾满了他们的血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种梦  我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}知识即是力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我叫艾莉丝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}这算是……什么恶梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你调查了我的过去啊  巴尔马公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}有时知情反而会产生恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.52,0:24:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}先让我看看吧--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}你是凯宾·雷古奈德的证明！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  纯白之黑